com.ibm.webest.gui.model
Class UseCaseItem

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.webest.gui.model.UseCaseItem
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class UseCaseItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class helps to create a tree for the UseCase-Table in GUI. You should initialize it with a list of UseCasePacks. Then the whole tree will build by itself, because a of UseCasePack contains all child-elements (UseCase) as a list. The class also calculates the uucp and total for all use cases. The logic for calculation is handled in processing and not in this class.

Author:
Florian Friedrichs
